{"tid":700787,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如何追唐琳玲等人走數？林鄭：考慮會否為某部份人帶來困難","createTime":"2018-06-13T15:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T15:29:24.000Z","uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c4364a77ddce554fb90eda199a2bddc6b3562847","tid":700787,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T15:29:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180613/58311830\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180613%2F58311830&d=RaTtOC72cGBplrU6jogn3xFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=c67cc6cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180613%2F58311830&h=29ba9c63\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180613/58311830</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥今早出席立法會答問環節，議員謝偉俊指早前內地人唐琳玲偷拍法庭未有付訟費就被遣返、吸煙罪行內地旅客欠交罰款及大學生拒還學費貸款等情況嚴重，形容香港如「無掩雞籠」成為「走數之都」，詢問林鄭會否有措施應對。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭回應指要「一方面要保障公帑」，另一方面亦要考慮追數時，會否為某部份人士帶來很大困難，尤其是大學生貸款問題，亦要考慮成本問題，指自己「好願意親自睇下個問題」。<br />\n謝偉俊就建議可以參考英國及日本做法。他強調，作為一個自由社會，不希望禁入出境如此嚴重，英國本身都由於早前有曼徹斯特個案，走數53萬英鎊，令當局也要考慮可能要限制非歐洲居民的服務，某些服務要先付錢才做；日本大阪府現在亦委託研究機構可以展開調查，減低「走數」機會，「當局會否跟進呢？令香港市民不要覺得我們今年加了這麼多公務員的人額，但我們的走數一樣這麼嚴重」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咪追我交稅, 仆街人生好困難呀</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 